{
  "stem": "18258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For that, I didn't need-- I didn't have to graduate from gymnasium or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It took four or five years, and then went to that school for five years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was called, that's the school where I went, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I graduated from there in electrotechnique.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at that time, we did not get the engineer's title.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was only arranged after the World War II, that the graduates of this particular school and parallel schools on several places in Vienna were allowed to carry the engineer's title.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Today, when I go to Vienna, I am Herr Engineer Snyder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by that time I had left the active party life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was involved in our store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we depended on general movement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not carrying the red flag anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also in 1933, I believe was the year when Chancellor Dollfuss got assassinated in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the assassins, I remember the name very well, was the son of the custodian of our apartment building.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how I knew the man's name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it struck me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had met him occasionally when they were here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he got hanged in Vienna for the assassination.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I remember the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hitler?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hitler was '38 already?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no, no, wait--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- that we found out later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I had found that out already when I was in the States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I visited Vienna later on in the '80s, I made it my business to go down and look at the house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is not even a plaque in front.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There might have been at one time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
